name: BoundedIterator_hasNextTest
description: Unit tests for the hasNext method of the BoundedIterator class.

test_cases.name: testHasNextWithinBounds
test_cases.description: Tests the hasNext method of BoundedIterator when the iterator is within bounds.

test_cases.name: testHasNextOutOfBounds

test_cases.description: Tests the hasNext method of BoundedIterator when there are no elements in the iterator.
